      ## Test plan

      To test the effectiveness of the button “What’s nearby”, I would measure the answers participants give to task 4:

      <em>“Without tapping anything yet, what do you think the button ‘What’s nearby’ does? Why?”</em>

      The participant needs to correctly identify that “What’s nearby” is for adding places to the map, <strong>before</strong> tapping on the button.

